ğŸ› ï¸ KaamSetu

KaamSetu is a real-time service platform that connects customers with nearby skilled workers such as plumbers, electricians, and carpenters. The platform focuses on speed, trust, and transparency using live location, instant notifications, OTP verification, and post-work payments.

ğŸš€ Problem Statement

Finding reliable local service workers is often slow, unorganized, and unsafe. Customers face delays, while workers miss opportunities due to lack of instant communication. There is no proper system to verify job completion or ensure fair payment.

ğŸ’¡ Solution

KaamSetu solves this by:

Instantly notifying nearby workers when a job is posted

Using live location to match customers and workers efficiently

Verifying worker arrival through OTP before work starts

Allowing payments only after job completion

This creates a fast, trusted, and real-world usable workflow.

ğŸ”„ Workflow Overview
Customer Flow

Login as Customer

Post a job with service details and live location

Track worker status in real time

Share OTP when worker reaches

Pay after job completion

Worker Flow

Login as Worker

Receive instant job notifications

Accept nearby jobs

Reach customer location and verify OTP

Complete job and receive payment

ğŸ”” Key Features

Real-time job notifications

Live location-based job matching

OTP-based job start verification

Clear job status flow

Mock payment after completion

Mobile-first, clean UI/UX

